---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Minecraft Server | Nieuserver.online</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background-color: #2a2a2a;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), 
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1587573089734-599851b0c8b6?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 250px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 0 20px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #2e8b57; /* Minecraft green */
        }
        
        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .card {
            background: #383838;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-left: 3px solid #2e8b57;
        }
        
        .card h2 {
            color: #2e8b57;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .card p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #b0b0b0;
        }
        
        footer {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 25px 0;
            margin-top: 50px;
            border-top: 2px solid #2e8b57;
        }
        
        nav {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #2e8b57;
        }
        
        nav ul {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        nav ul li a {
            color: #e0e0e0;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        
        nav ul li a:hover {
            color: #2e8b57;
        }
        
        .active {
            color: #2e8b57;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .server-info {
            background: #2a2a2a;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: monospace;
            border: 1px solid #2e8b57;
        }
        
        .rules li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header {
                height: 200px;
            }
            
            header h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/minecraft" class="active">Minecraft</a></li>
            <li><a href="/terraria">Terraria</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    
    <header>
        <h1>Nieuserver Minecraft</h1>
        <p>A simple survival server with basic plugins</p>
    </header>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Server Information</h2>
            <div class="server-info">
                <p><strong>Address:</strong> minecraft.nieuserver.online</p>
                <p><strong>Version:</strong> 1.20.4 (Java Edition)</p>
                <p><strong>Status:</strong> Online (20 player slots)</p>
                <p><strong>Uptime:</strong> ~95% (restarts daily at 4 AM UTC)</p>
            </div>
            <p>This is a standard PaperMC survival server with minimal plugins to keep gameplay close to vanilla.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Features</h2>
            <ul class="rules">
                <li>Survival mode with land claiming</li>
                <li>No pay-to-win elements</li>
                <li>Basic anti-grief protections</li>
                <li>Dynmap available at: <code>map.nieuserver.online</code></li>
                <li>Regular world backups</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Rules</h2>
            <ul class="rules">
                <li>No griefing or stealing</li>
                <li>PvP must be consensual</li>
                <li>No hacked clients</li>
                <li>Keep chat family-friendly</li>
                <li>Respect staff decisions</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Breaking rules may result in temporary or permanent bans.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>How to Join</h2>
            <ol class="rules">
                <li>Launch Minecraft Java Edition 1.20.4</li>
                <li>Click "Multiplayer" then "Add Server"</li>
                <li>Enter <code>minecraft.nieuserver.online</code> as the address</li>
                <li>Click "Done" then select the server to join</li>
            </ol>
            <p>No whitelist - just connect and play.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 nieuserver.online</p>
        <p>Minecraft is a trademark of Mojang Studios</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>